metadata.name: Within Your Eyes
metadata.description:
" In your eyes i saw a speck of the sun beaming in the sky, 
  and in Yours eyes, I learned how it was possible to get so 
  very lost,
  In your eyes I witnessed something beyond the 
  explanation of this mortal world 
  I will keep looking for you until I find you 
  Eyes beaming with life and beyond "
